&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Your Opportunity&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Scion is paving a path in student living and we’re seeking an Area Manager to join us in executing our vision. This position manages the operations for a portfolio of properties and is accountable for carrying out the strategic objectives set in place by the Regional Manager. The Area Manager assesses risk, creates appropriate strategies, and implements successful solutions with their teams.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
