&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who is Scion?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As one of North America’s leading owners, operators and advisors of student housing, we are defining the future of student living. From operations to accounting, brand to software engineering, we’re building a team to help us take student living to the next level.&lt;/p&gt;
