&lt;p&gt;The BI Analyst executes complex data analysis and reporting initiatives. This role partners closely with business leaders to define requirements, design dashboards, and provide actionable insights that support strategic and operational decision-making.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Your Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Independently gather, integrate, and validate data from multiple internal and external sources&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design and maintain interactive dashboards and scalable reporting solutions in Excel, Looker, and other BI tools&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Perform advanced trend analysis and statistical evaluation to identify business drivers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Translate business requirements into SQL queries, data models, and analytical frameworks&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deliver data-driven recommendations to improve performance and operational outcomes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support ad hoc analytic and scenario modeling requests&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work closely with Data Science and Data Engineering to support reporting needs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Serve as key analytics partner to various business units&lt;/li&gt;
